Design Explanation

1. Separation of Concerns
Student handles user identity
UserAccount handles authentication
This improves security and maintainability

2. Composition Relationships
A Module contains Assignments
An Assignment has a Deadline
These are strong ownership relationships

3. Association Relationships
Assignments trigger Notifications
Dashboard aggregates assignments for display

4. Multiplicity
One student -> many modules
One module ->  many assignments
One assignment ->  many notifications


Use Cases ->  Create Assignment, View Dashboard
State Diagrams ->  Assignment lifecycle Activity Diagrams ->  Notification workflow
User Stories ->  US-04, US-05, US-08
